<head>Died.</head> 
<div4 type="obit" n="1" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="319" /> On yesterday, after a long and painful illness, which she bore with truly <name>Christian</name> fortitude and resignation, <persName n="Sangster,Mrs.,Mary,K.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00192" reg="default:Sangster,Mary,K.,," authname="sangster,mary,k."><roleName n="Mrs." full="yes">Mrs.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">Mary</foreName> <foreName full="yes">K.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Sangster</surname></persName>, consort of <persName n="Sangster,Mister,Edward,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00193" reg="default:Sangster,Edward,,," authname="sangster,edward"><roleName n="Mister" full="yes">Mr.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">Edward</foreName> <surname full="yes">Sangster</surname></persName>, of <placeName reg="Alexandria, Alexandria, Virginia" key="tgn,7013269" authname="tgn,7013269">Alexandria</placeName>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="320" /> The friends of the family are invited to attend her funeral to-day at <time value="3pm">3 o'clock P. M.</time>, from her husband's residence, west end of <address><street n="Clay street">Clay street</street></address>, near <placeName reg="Buchanan's Spring">Buchanan's Spring</placeName>. </p> </div4> 
<div4 type="obit" n="2" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="321" /> On <date>Thursday</date>, the <dateStruct value="--12" full="yes" authname="---12"><day reg="12" full="yes">12th instant</day></dateStruct>, at <time value="9pm">9 o'clock P. M.</time>, after a lingering illness, contracted in the service, <persName n="Drumheller,,John,L.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00194" reg="default:Drumheller,John,L.,," authname="drumheller,john,l."><foreName full="yes">John</foreName> <foreName full="yes">L.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Drumheller</surname></persName>, aged <measure n="31years" type="date">thirty-one years</measure>, leaving an affectionate wife and interesting little daughter to mourn their loss. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="322" /> The friends and acquaintances of the family are respectfully requested to attend his funeral from <placeName reg="Clay Street Chapel">Clay Street Chapel</placeName> on to-morrow (<dateStruct full="yes"><day type="name" full="yes">Sunday</day></dateStruct>) at <time value="3pm">3 o'clock P. M.</time> </p> </div4> </div3> </div2> 
